articles.author: Associated Press
articles.title: Space telescope launched on daring quest to behold first stars - 9News
articles.description: NASA's James Webb Space Telescope soared from French Guiana on South America’s northeastern coast, riding a European Ariane rocket into the Christmas morning sky.
